&lt;p&gt;We have exciting opportunities for Operating Department Practitioners within our Theatre complex. We have 9 Theatres at Worthing including a busy Obstetric unit as well as a Day Surgery unit and Ophthalmology department at Southlands Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our departments are supported by Practice Development and we are able to offer a wide variety of in-house training related to clinical skills and your personal development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our nationally recognized Patient First Improvement system ensures that all members of our staff are actively encouraged to contribute to making improvements in their areas of work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;come join our &lt;em&gt;Outstanding Trust&lt;/em&gt; or discuss further please contact&lt;/p&gt;
